{"tid":2016935,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"教育局幾時譴責埋毛澤東/中央文獻版社/人民出版社/人民網 傷害中國人民感情","createTime":"2020-05-14T19:09:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T07:23:34.000Z","uid":36901,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"81475854d7e9f08a3a0bfed7c50a77f278768ee8","tid":2016935,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T19:09:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.people.com.cn/GB/shizheng/8198/30446/30452/2195605.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.people.com.cn%2FGB%2Fshizheng%2F8198%2F30446%2F30452%2F2195605.html&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7pX8N1KgQotyuydbLhb69C0%3D&h=a5b1b454\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.people.com.cn/GB/shizheng/8198/30446/30452/2195605.html</a><br />\n<br />\n日本的南鄉三郎見我時，一見面就說:日本侵略了中國，對不住你們。 我對他說:我們不這樣看，是日本軍閥佔領了大半個中國，因此教育了中國人民，不然中國人民不會覺悟，不會團結，那末我們到現在也還在山上，不能到北京來看 京戲。 就是因為日本&ldquo;皇軍&rdquo;佔領了大半個中國，中國人民別無出路，才覺悟起來，才武裝起來進行鬥爭，建立了許多抗日根據地，為解放戰爭的勝利創造了條件。 所以日本軍閥、壟斷資本乾了件好事，<span style=\"color: red;\">如果要感謝的話，我寧願感謝日本軍閥</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&ldquo;我同很多日本朋友講過這段事情，其中一部分人說日本侵略中國不好。我說侵略當然不好，但不能單看這壞的一面，另一面日本幫了我們中國的大忙。假如日本不佔領大半個中國，中國人民不會覺醒起來。在這一點上，我們<span style=\"color: red;\">要&lsquo;感謝&rsquo;日本&lsquo;皇軍&rsquo;。</span>&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n《毛澤東外交文選》第534頁"},{"pid":"2222b9d72bce1ac7bad89d4c8b3c65c57337f3c7","tid":2016935,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T19:11:53.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"fa9749c8920427bfc29516668642f83c33253923","tid":2016935,"uid":36901,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T19:16:31.000Z","msg":"我說侵略當然不好，但不能單看這壞的一面，另一面日本幫了我們中國的大忙。假如日本不佔領大半個中國，中國人民不會覺醒起來。在這一點上，我們要&lsquo;感謝&rsquo;日本&lsquo;皇軍&rsquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n毛澤東呢句說話簡直係掌摑教育局/保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49a1c72740c9ac1dc0eda0bd5af9f9bc8f2970ef","tid":2016935,"uid":6942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T19:23:48.000Z","msg":"唔好問呀 班官員會hang機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff63434e695aa9aa1e3352f3557d0188ef0d9e16","tid":2016935,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-14T19:38:39.000Z","msg":"鳳凰衛視話日本人支持近代中國革命<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2016928\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2016928</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有唔好漏左譴責鳳凰衛視，正黑記<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85de36573e729f62b81806128987e0b1160589bd","tid":2016935,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14776c165ba215ac507c35c77e00a64ac86cc2d0","tid":2016935,"uid":41998,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T00:46:54.000Z","msg":"【#突發】指鹿為馬、文革2.0新常態。教育局局長應評論毛主席的話：<br />\n<br />\n「日本皇軍過去佔領了大半個中國，因此中國人民接受了教育。如果沒有日本的侵略，我們現在還在山裏，就不能到北京看京劇了。正是因為日本皇軍佔領了大半個中國，讓我們建立了許多抗日根據地，為以後的解放戰爭創造了勝利的條件。日本壟斷資本和軍閥給我們做了件『好事』，如果需要感謝的話，我倒想感謝日本皇軍侵略中國。」<br />\n<br />\n- 毛澤東，1961年1月24日，會見日本社會黨議員黑田壽男等人談話，記載於《毛澤東外交文選》<br />\n<br />\n▶️ 文革2.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8tlEKYQ2asE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D8tlEKYQ2asE&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7pX8N1KgQotyuydbLhb69C0%3D&h=e465a4f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8tlEKYQ2asE</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3260673430633451&amp;id=223783954322429\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D3260673430633451%26id%3D223783954322429&d=i3QdlbdnIScuB0pxdHOU7pX8N1KgQotyuydbLhb69C0%3D&h=10502efd\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=3260673430633451&amp;id=223783954322429</a>"},{"pid":"a0a80b919bf608d46db666293fbf59fdad178e5d","tid":2016935,"uid":41998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:03:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68f2e7c4e19ae793d32aa85b5f5d178d078a6a0f","tid":2016935,"uid":140802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T03:03:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba237000b0e478a49af39f6777a27b60997296a","tid":2016935,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T07:23:34.000Z","msg":"作反"}]}